---
// Product overview section for Smallest
---

<section class="product-overview">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="overview-grid">
      <div class="overview-text">
        <h2>L'astronomie nomade sans compromis</h2>
        <p>
          Le Smallest donne un sens à l'astronomie nomade en combinant les performances d'un télescope 150/750 
          avec une forte portabilité. Conçu pour les astronomes qui refusent de choisir entre qualité 
          optique et mobilité.
        </p>
        <div class="overview-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">l25cm x L25cm x H20cm </span>
            <span class="stat-label">Structure en format transport</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">l6cm x L87cm</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Tiges en format transport</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">4kg</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Poids total</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="overview-video">
        <video autoplay loop muted playsinline>
          <source src="/assets/tp 150750.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          <p>Votre navigateur ne prend pas en charge les vidéos HTML5.</p>
        </video>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .product-overview {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--gray-900);
  }

  .overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .overview-text h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--gray-100);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .overview-text p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--gray-300);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .overview-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-regular);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }

  .overview-video video {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .overview-stats {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>